name: Galen Marek, Starkiller
Lore: '''Perhaps you are not as strong as the Emperor thought.''',
Text: 'Galen''s forfeit may not be reduced. Power and defense value +2 while with Mariss Brood. If defending a battle alone (or defending with Juno Eclipse), may be targeted by Force Lightning. Immune to Clash Of Sabers and attrition < 4.',
